<img src="http://www.bizcommunity.com/c/1804/437750-625x156.png" alt="The art of the site visit" width="625" height="156">The venue is the one item on your list that can tie all your event details together. This can have a huge impact on how your guests gather and what they experience. We like to think that selecting a venue is both a science and an art. The science being the usage of information at hand to decipher the suitability of the venue, while the art is the event planner’s instinct and connection with a space. This may seem like a romantic notion, but when you’ve been in the industry a long time your instincts about certain things - like venues - automatically come alive. Once you’ve identified potential venues for your event, the next step is to narrow your options by physically visiting the site...To read the full article visit our blog: https://www.wrxgrp.co.za/art-site-visit/